PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1986-1/2914 of December 18, 1986, as amended, which will extend the duration of the FARM DEBT REVIEW PROGRAM until March 31, 1992, a program under which payments are made to the Farm Credit Corporation on behalf of individual farmers in accordance with arrangements made between those farmers and the Farm Credit Corporation.
